{"id": "art-1121", "label": "Art. 1121", "title": "Art. 1121: Confiscarea extinsă", "slug": "art-1121", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1082948449\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1410\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1082948449\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 112<sup>1</sup>:\nConfiscarea extins&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1155005183\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1409\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1155005183\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Sunt supuse confisc&#259;rii &#351;i alte bunuri decât\ncele prev&#259;zute la art. 112, când fa&#355;&#259; de o persoan&#259; se\ndispune condamnarea pentru o fapt&#259; susceptibil&#259; s&#259; îi procure un\nfolos material &#351;i pentru care pedeapsa prev&#259;zut&#259; de lege este\nînchisoarea de 4 ani sau mai mare, instan&#355;a î&#351;i formeaz&#259;\nconvingerea c&#259; bunurile respective provin din activit&#259;&#355;i\ninfrac&#355;ionale. Convingerea instan&#355;ei se poate baza inclusiv pe dispropor&#355;ia\ndintre veniturile licite &#351;i averea persoanei.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1113659860\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1408\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1113659860\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Confiscarea extins&#259; se dispune asupra bunurilor\ndobândite de persoana condamnat&#259; într-o perioad&#259; de 5 ani înainte\n&#351;i, dac&#259; este cazul, dup&#259; momentul s&#259;vâr&#351;irii\ninfrac&#355;iunii, pân&#259; la data emiterii actului de sesizare a\ninstan&#355;ei. Confiscarea extins&#259; poate fi dispus&#259; &#351;i asupra\nbunurilor transferate c&#259;tre ter&#355;i, dac&#259; ace&#351;tia &#351;tiau\nsau ar fi trebuit s&#259; &#351;tie c&#259; scopul transferului a fost evitarea\nconfisc&#259;rii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1897314880\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1407\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1897314880\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Pentru aplicarea dispozi&#355;iilor alin. (2) se va\n&#355;ine seama &#351;i de valoarea bunurilor transferate de c&#259;tre\npersoana condamnat&#259; ori de un ter&#355; unui membru al familiei sau unei\npersoane juridice asupra c&#259;reia persoana condamnat&#259; de&#355;ine\ncontrolul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_837564023\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1406\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_837564023\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Prin bunuri, conform prezentului articol, se\nîn&#355;elege &#351;i sumele de bani.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_119229091\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1405\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_119229091\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)La stabilirea diferen&#355;ei dintre veniturile licite\n&#351;i valoarea bunurilor dobândite se vor avea în vedere valoarea bunurilor\nla data dobândirii lor &#351;i cheltuielile f&#259;cute de persoana\ncondamnat&#259;, membrii familiei acesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_179302480\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1404\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_179302480\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Dac&#259; bunurile supuse confisc&#259;rii nu se\ng&#259;sesc, în locul lor se confisc&#259; bani &#351;i bunuri pân&#259; la\nconcuren&#355;a valorii acestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_125332368\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1403\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_125332368\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Se confisc&#259;, de asemenea, bunurile &#351;i banii\nob&#355;inu&#355;i din exploatarea sau folosirea bunurilor supuse\nconfisc&#259;rii, precum &#351;i bunurile produse de acestea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_96441916\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1402\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_96441916\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Confiscarea nu poate dep&#259;&#351;i valoarea bunurilor\ndobândite în perioada prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (2), care excedeaz&#259;\nnivelului veniturilor licite ale persoanei condamnate.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>TITLUL V:Minoritatea</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL I:Regimul r&#259;spunderii penale a\nminorului</span></b></p>"}